&lt;p data-start=&quot;664&quot; data-end=&quot;1567&quot;&gt;As the Director of Education Services at Ridgeline, you will lead and scale a growing learning organization responsible for training CX employees, services partners, and customer end-users on our modern, enterprise-grade AI platform for investment and wealth management. Reporting to the Director of Customer Success and Education Services, you will oversee a high-performing team while shaping the strategy, structure, technology stack, and commercial model of Ridgeline’s evolving education offerings. You will design scalable programs, define success metrics, and ensure operational excellence to deliver meaningful customer outcomes and business impact. You will leverage modern learning methodologies and AI-enabled tools—including ChatGPT and Claude—to enhance program design, improve efficiency, and elevate learning experiences across our ecosystem.&lt;/p&gt;
