&lt;li class=&quot;li4&quot;&gt;Collaborate with FIX infrastructure partners like Broadridge’s Itiviti and NYFIX Trading Hub to deploy and maintain FIX connectivity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li4&quot;&gt;Own the configuration and customization of FIX messages, tags, and protocols aligned with Ridgeline’s OMS&lt;/li&gt;
